    <title>机器学习-凸优化</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2017/10/25/article-title/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2017/10/25/article-title/</id>
    <published>2017-10-25T06:47:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-10-30T03:41:08.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">printf(&quot;hello Markdown!&quot;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Convex"><a href="#Convex" class="headerlink" title="Convex"></a>Convex</h1><p>&#x51F8;&#x51FD;&#x6570;(convex)&#xFF1A;  </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(\mathbf{y}) \geq f(\mathbf{x}) + \nabla f(\mathbf{x}) ^ {T} (\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x})</script></blockquote><p>&#x5F3A;&#x51F8;&#x51FD;&#x6570;(strongly-convex)&#xFF1A;   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(\mathbf{y}) \geq f(\mathbf{x}) + \nabla f(\mathbf{x}) ^ {T} (\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}) + \frac{m}{2}||\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}||^2</script></blockquote><p>L-Lipschitz   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">f(\mathbf{y}) \leq f(\mathbf{x}) + \nabla f(\mathbf{x}) ^ {T} (\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}) + \frac{L}{2}||\mathbf{y}-\mathbf{x}||^2</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Leftrightarrow |\nabla f(x) -\nabla f(x) < L||x-y|| |</script></blockquote><p>&#x5E73;&#x65B9;&#x635F;&#x5931;(square-loss):  $y \in \mathbb{R}$   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) = \frac{1}{2}(y_i-h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta))^2</script><p>&#x5176;&#x4E2D;&#x5728;&#x7EBF;&#x6027;&#x56DE;&#x5F52;&#x4E2D; &#xFF0C;$h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta) = \theta^T \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i$)     </p></blockquote><p>&#x5BF9;&#x6570;&#x635F;&#x5931;(logistic loss):   $y  \in {-1,1}$      </p><blockquote><p>$l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) = log(1+exp(-y_i h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)))$   </p></blockquote><p>&#x4E00;&#x9636;&#x5BFC;&#x6570;(one order of diff of square-loss)       </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\nabla_{\mathbf{x}_i} l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) = \frac{\partial l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta))}{\partial \theta} = (y_i-h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta)) \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i)</script></blockquote><p>&#x4E8C;&#x9636;&#x5BFC;&#x6570;(two order of diff of square-loss)</p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\frac{\partial \nabla_{\mathbf{x}_i} l(y_i,h(\mathbf{x}_i,\theta))}{ \partial \theta } = \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i)^T</script></blockquote><p>&#x2014; &#x6C42;&#x4E8C;&#x9636;Hessian&#x77E9;&#x9635;&#x7684;&#x7279;&#x5F81;&#x503C;:   </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i)^T \mathbf{z} = \lambda \mathbf{z}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">(\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) ^T \mathbf{z})\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) = \lambda \mathbf{z}</script><p>&#x56E0;&#x6B64;&#x5F97;&#x5230;&#xFF1A;   </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\mathbf{z} = k \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \quad k \neq 0</script><p>&#x4EE3;&#x5165;&#x4E0A;&#x5F0F;&#x5F97;&#x5230;&#xFF1A;   </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\lambda = \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) ^T \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \geq 0</script></blockquote><p><span style="color:blue">s&#x6240;&#x4EE5;&#x5E73;&#x65B9;&#x635F;&#x5931;(square-loss)&#x662F;&#x51F8;&#x51FD;&#x6570;&#xFF0C;&#x82E5;$\Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) ^T \Phi (\mathbf{x}_i) \geq c ,c&gt;0.$&#x90A3;&#x4E48;&#x5E73;&#x65B9;&#x635F;&#x5931;(square-loss)&#x662F;&#x5F3A;&#x51F8;&#x51FD;&#x6570;</span></p><hr><h1 id="Lasso"><a href="#Lasso" class="headerlink" title="Lasso"></a>Lasso</h1><p>&#x5BF9;&#x4E8E;&#x4F18;&#x5316;&#x76EE;&#x6807;&#xFF1A;</p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\min \limits_x f(x) + \lambda||x||_1</script><p>&#x4F7F;&#x7528;&#x8FD1;&#x7AEF;&#x68AF;&#x5EA6;&#x4E0B;&#x964D;(PGD)&#x6C42;&#x89E3;&#xFF0C;&#x6709;&#x95ED;&#x5F0F;&#x89E3;&#xFF1A;</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">x_{k+1}^i = \begin{cases}   z^i-\lambda/L &\text{if } z^i>\lambda/L  \\   0 &\text{if } -\lambda/L < z^i < \lambda/L \\   z^i+\lambda/L &\text{if } z^i < -\lambda/L\end{cases}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\text{其中} \quad \mathbf{z} = \mathbf{x}_k - \frac{1}{L} \nabla f(\mathbf{x}_k)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\nabla f \text{满足L-lipschitz条件}, L \text{为L-lipschitz常数}</script><p>&#x6240;&#x4EE5;L1-norm&#x4F1A;&#x4EA7;&#x751F;&#x7A00;&#x758F;&#x89E3;&#xFF0C;&#x4E14;$\lambda$&#x8D8A;&#x5927;&#xFF0C;&#x4EA7;&#x751F;&#x7684;&#x89E3;&#x8D8A;&#x7A00;&#x758F;&#x3002;</p></blockquote><p>group-lasso  </p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\min \limits_x f(x) + \sum_{j=1}^J\lambda||x_j||_{K_j}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">x_j \text{是x的一个子集} ||x_j||_{K_j }= x_j^TK_jx_j,K_j \text{是半正定矩阵}</script><p>&#x4F7F;&#x7528;PGD&#x6C42;&#x89E3;&#x53EF;&#x80FD;&#x4EA7;&#x751F;&#x5168;&#x96F6;&#x89E3;&#xFF1B;&#x6CE8;&#x610F;$K_j = I$&#x65F6;&#xFF0C;&#x5BF9;&#x5E94;l2-norm&#x4E0D;&#x5E26;&#x5E73;&#x65B9;&#x3002;</p></blockquote><h1 id="PCA-&#x4E3B;&#x6210;&#x5206;&#x5206;&#x6790;"><a href="#PCA-&#x4E3B;&#x6210;&#x5206;&#x5206;&#x6790;" class="headerlink" title="PCA(&#x4E3B;&#x6210;&#x5206;&#x5206;&#x6790;)"></a>PCA(&#x4E3B;&#x6210;&#x5206;&#x5206;&#x6790;)</h1><p>&#x7528;&#x4E8E;&#x77E9;&#x9635;&#x5206;&#x89E3;&#xFF1A;</p><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\text{求出} d'\text{个特征向量,表示成矩阵} W,W \text{的每一行对应一个特征向量;}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\text{原始数据}X \text{的每一列对应一个数据点}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">WX \text{低维空间的数据表示}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">W^TWX \text{原始空间的重构数据表示}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\text{因此PCA把原始数据矩阵X分解成两个小矩阵} W^T,WX.</script></blockquote><h1 id="Convlution-GEMM"><a href="#Convlution-GEMM" class="headerlink" title="Convlution(GEMM)"></a>Convlution(GEMM)</h1><blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">W_{n,c,m,k} \text{表示卷积核的第n个filter,第c个channel，(m,k)的2D-filter的相对位置,令}W_{i,:,:,:} \text{为列向量}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">W_{reshape} = \begin{bmatrix}   W_{1,:,:,:} , W_{2,:,:,:} ...... W_{n,:,:,:}\end{bmatrix}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\text{卷积操作可以表示成矩阵乘法：}Y = im2col(X)  W_{reshape},\text{矩阵Y的每一列代表一个feature map.}</script></blockquote>]]></content>
    
